Class SPARQL

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Handler

    public final class SPARQL
extends Endpoint<SPARQL>
    SPARQL 1.1 Query/Update endpoint handler.

    Provides a standard SPARQL 1.1 Query/Update endpoint exposing the contents of the system graph database.

    Both query and update operations are restricted to users in the root role, unless otherwise specified.

    See Also:
    SPARQL 1.1 Protocol
